TypeSignature.Value: .class public auto ansi beforefieldinit PropertyCollection extends System.Object implements class System.Collections.IEnumerable

Docs.summary: Represents a collection of Property objects.

remarks.para: Use the class to enumerate all properties defined at a site.

example.para: The following code example shows the use of the class.
example.code:
Public Sub SectionSample() 'Get portal site context from topology. Dim strUrl As String = "http://SampleName" Dim tm As New TopologyManager() Dim ps As PortalSite = tm.PortalSites(New Uri(strUrl)) Dim pc As PortalContext = PortalApplication.GetContext(ps)
'Initialize user profile config manager object. Dim upcm As New UserProfileConfigManager(pc)
'Sample to create a new section. Dim pcol As PropertyCollection = upcm.GetPropertiesWithSection() Dim mysection As [Property] = pcol.Create(True) mysection.Name = "my section" mysection.Commit() pcol.SetDisplayOrderBySectionName(mysection.Name, 0) pcol.CommitDisplayOrder() End Sub 'SectionSample
